## Getting Started

```bash
# 1. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 2. Pull the LLM model
ollama pull gemma:2b

# 3. Add medical documents to datasets/
#    (PDFs, .txt, .md files)

# 4. Run the application
python main.py

# 5. Select option 6 to build the knowledge base first
#    Then use any other option for consultations
```
